text: Anchal Kumar (born 24 October 1979) is an Indian actress, supermodel, influencer, and beauty pageant winner. She won the Gladrags Manhunt and Megamodel Contest and represented India at Miss Intercontinental 1999. She has also acted in Bollywood films like Fashion and Bluffmaster!.
